author: Unreal Engine
description:
Watch this session recorded at Unreal Fest Orlando 2025 and explore the new features and improvements in Unreal Engine 5.6 for mobile game development. 

We cover tools and workflows for building and debugging on Android and iOS, as well as the rendering capabilities of Unreal Engine on mobile devices.

Want to find out more about creating mobile games in Unreal Engine? Take a look here: unrealengine.com/uses/mobile-games

title: Mobile Game Development with Unreal Engine | Unreal Fest Orlando 2025

author: Unreal Engine
description:
Watch this session recorded at Unreal Fest Orlando 2025 to see what’s coming down the pipe for Unreal Engine.

In this video, we take a dive into the Unreal Engine roadmap and give you an insight into where Epic is spending development time.

Get a peek at the tools and improvements coming to UE 5.6 across all areas of the engine—as well as a look further ahead to some of the exciting features in development for future releases.

Check out the Unreal Engine public roadmap here: portal.productboard.com/epicgames/1-unreal-engine-public-roadmap/tabs/124-unreal-engine-5-6

#PublicRoadmap #UE5.6, #UnrealEngine, #UE5, #UnrealFestOrlando
title: A Peek at Some Future Features Coming to Unreal Engine | Unreal Fest Orlando 2025
